---
description: Ship all connector UI CSS/JS in-package — never rely on the host site
globs: **/*.{php,blade.php,css,js}
alwaysApply: true
---

# Self-contained assets

Host apps do not compile this package’s Tailwind and must not be expected to
provide layout CSS or JS for the connector admin UI.

- Put layout/visual CSS in the package (scoped `<style>` in Blade with a `ga-*`
  prefix, or a published CSS file loaded by the plugin/page).
- Filament components are fine for Filament-owned chrome; do not rely on utility
  classes (`flex`, `grid`, `gap-*`, etc.) unless defined in package CSS.
- Do not assume the host’s `app.css`, Vite, or Tailwind content paths include
  these views.
